data.description: Welcome to this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo near Parkfield Lake Park! This main floor unit offers a comfortable and convenient layout with no stairs and is located just minutes away from Pena Blvd, for easy commuting and access to nearby shopping, dining, and entertainment. The open floor plan features a cozy living room with gas fireplace and private patio access ~ perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or evening relaxation. Dining space leads into the open kitchen with ample storage. This condo boasts two spacious bedrooms, including a primary suite with an ensuite full bathroom with double vanities, as well as walk-in closets providing plenty of room for storage. Laundry closet in unit. As part of the community you'll have access to a range of amenities such as a fitness center, swimming pool, and a clubhouse for gatherings. Additionally, the condo comes with reserved parking, ensuring convenience and peace of mind. Parkfield Lake Park is just a short walk away! Enjoy the greenery, walking trails, and recreational activities offered by the park. Don't miss out on this great condo- schedule your private showing today!
